attributes.title: Surviving a Zombie Attack for 7 Minutes
attributes.caption: We just wanted to play a nice game of 7 Days To Die, but Jack had to go and get turned into a zombie.
attributes.description:
This video is sponsored by PC Game Pass! Game Pass HAS PC Games! Check it out here: https://xbox.com/pcgamepass
We just wanted to play a nice game of 7 Days To Die, but Jack had to go and get turned into a zombie.. Can Trevor, Michael, Alfredo, and Ky survive against a zombie for 7 minutes, or will Zombie Jack and his friends find them all?

attributes.title: It’s Jeopardy But With Eggs! - Egg Jeopardy!
attributes.caption: Welcome to Egg Jeopardy! A legally-distinct game show where contestants match the questions to the answers, but also with eggs! This week, Joe, Alfredo, and Kayla see what tricks Trevor has hatched up for them.

attributes.title: We Tricked A Store Into Selling Our Photos - OutDorks
attributes.caption: Trevor and Joe take their Between the Games antics to the streets in OutDorks! This week, Trevor tries to find a way to live out his dream of being a stock photo model. Can their photos slip under the radar, or will his dream become a nightmare.

attributes.caption: Hope you brought your appetite, it’s time for Egg Jeopardy! A legally-distinct game show where contestants match the questions to the answers, but also with eggs. This week, Trevor tests Ky, BK, and Michael on movie lines, sports teams, and fighting off Mr. Rooster.

attributes.title: Summer Bois Mix - AH Remix
attributes.caption: It’s the middle of summer, it’s way too hot outside, but luckily, the Summer Bois are here to keep things cool. The Play Pals aka Team Nice Dynamite aka Gavin and Michael are here to doo do do do do and ah ah ah ah ah their way through the oppressive heat of summer with this Super Bunny Man remix.

attributes.title: You Laugh, You Lose: Interrogation Room Improv
attributes.caption: This is Don’t Make A Scene, our take on a try not to laugh challenge! Each episode has a different scenario that the gang has to improvise a scene in and if they laugh, they lose. Let’s see how much Michael, Trevor, Alfredo, and Joe can handle in the interrogation room.
